## CNMP — Sistema de Resoluções (webservice REST com HTTP Basic Auth)
## Solicitar usuário com perfil "Web Service": sistemasresolucoes@cnmp.mp.br
CNMP_USER=seu_usuario
CNMP_PASSWORD=sua_senha

## Azure AD / OAuth2 (Service Principal para Fabric)
CLIENT_ID=xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx
CLIENT_SECRET=sua_client_secret
TENANT_ID=xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx

## Microsoft Fabric — Lakehouse (arquivos brutos)
FABRIC_WORKSPACE_ID=xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx
FABRIC_LAKEHOUSE_NAME=mp_raw

## Microsoft Fabric — Warehouse (tabelas estruturadas)
FABRIC_WAREHOUSE_HOST=xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx.datawarehouse.fabric.microsoft.com
FABRIC_WAREHOUSE_NAME=mp_warehouse
